  "detailed_description": "In <strong>Sleepy Heroes you</strong> can try to create the best <strong>synergy</strong> in each round. You can complete your rounds like <strong>solving a puzzle</strong> by sorting your cards, and face off against sleepy creatures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/8af8313a94297c849a2cfcd32c2e0d2e.poster.avif?t=1727424352\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/8af8313a94297c849a2cfcd32c2e0d2e.webm?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/8af8313a94297c849a2cfcd32c2e0d2e.mp4?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Like solving a puzzle!</strong></h2>In <strong>Auto-Battler</strong> style battles, you can sit back and <strong>relax</strong> with the special mechanic of sequencing your cards in order. The <strong>order in which you play</strong> cards is very important in Sleepy Heroes. Grasp this original mechanic to create <strong>great combos</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/9a7f466e9cb7c97b497eff348f0889c4.poster.avif?t=1727424352\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/9a7f466e9cb7c97b497eff348f0889c4.webm?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164490/extras/9a7f466e9cb7c97b497eff348f0889c4.mp4?t=1727424352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In each battle, choose <strong>temporary cards</strong> and try them out. Build your strategy by adding <strong>permanent cards</strong> when you win a battle.<br>Power up your deck with dozens of different <strong>Trinkets</strong>.<br>Make choices in <strong>events</strong> and <strong>shops</strong>. Defeat tough elites to reach the <strong>last boss</strong>.<br>Enjoy <strong>Lo-Fi</strong> music and capture different synergies over and over again.",
